      "kind": "line",
      "who": "亲戚叔父",
      "voice": {
        "id": "MOBA_001_PRO001K_007",
        "file": "voice/moba_001_pro001K_007.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「怎么样？感觉很舒适，是个相当不错的店吧？」"
